.TH AI-PLAYBOOK-SHOW 1 "" "ai-playbook" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ai\-playbook\-show \- Render a saved playbook read\-only
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBai\-playbook\fR show <slug>
.SH DESCRIPTION
show renders a saved playbook read\-only in the pager (no run, no edit affordance beyond [edit]).
.SH OPTIONS
This command takes no flags.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
ai\-playbook show deploy\-staging
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBai\-playbook\fR(1)
